v0.1.2.description:
### New Features
- The list of custom keybinds for QoL changes (F8 for Level Selection menu, F11 for mobile Storage Box access) is now listed underneath the Archipelago server entry field
### Bug Fixes
- Fixed multiple issues where key items would disappear after being picked up if they were placed into a puzzle such as the Plate items, Ring items, etc.
- Fixed a visual bug that resulted in two Elsters being shown if the player loaded into the Penrose Wreck using the Level Selection menu
- Fixed a logic issue that resulted in unbeatable seeds
- Fixed an issue where one-sided doors would have to be re-unlocked if the player reloaded a level through the Level Selection menu

[README](https://github.com/devoidlazarus/SIGNALISArchipelagoRandomizer/blob/main/README.md)*
